dct_description_sm: Compiled from the latest information ; published Feb. 1890, at the Hydrographic Office under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings and isolines.
Tides note, Floating Docks table (Tanjung Priok Hr.).
Shows shoals, reefs, drainage, islands, vegetation, channels, buildings, various buildings and facilities, roads, railroads.
